message.content:
1. Participants not ready to quit in the next 30 days are in Precontemplation or Contemplation stages.
2. Participants in Precontemplation or Contemplation stages engaged most when prompted to think about the pros and cons of behavior change.
3. Participants in the Preparation stage engaged most when posts increased awareness about smoking and smoking cessation.
